# Tokra Shield

Lightweight, dependency‑free content‑protection SDK (spam, scam, prompt‑injection).

## Install
```bash
pip install tokra-shield
```

## Use in code
```python
from tokra_shield import analyze
print(analyze("click here to win free crypto!", lang="en"))
```

## CLI
```bash
tokra-shield check "free crypto now"
tokra-shield run  # REST API on :8099
```

## API (POST /analyze/)
```json
{ "text": "click here", "lang": "en" }
```

Apache‑2.0
